    <div class="bg-white p-4 rounded-lg shadow flex flex-col space-y-4">
      
      <!-- Edit Nickname -->
      <div class="flex flex-col">
        <h4 class="font-semibold text-lg">Nickname</h4>
        <input type="text" id="nickname" class="text-sm p-2 rounded-lg border mt-2" placeholder="Enter new nickname" />
        <button id="saveNickname" class="mt-2 bg-green-600 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded hover:bg-green-700">Save</button>
      </div>

      <!-- Brightness Adjustment -->
      <div class="flex flex-col">
        <h4 class="font-semibold text-lg">Adjust Brightness</h4>

      <!-- Font Size Adjustment -->
      <div class="flex flex-col">

        <input type="range" id="fontSizeSlider" min="12" max="24" value="16" class="mt-2" />
        <p id="fontSizeValue" class="text-sm text-gray-600">16px</p>
      </div>

    </div>

    <!-- Change Password -->
    <a href="change-password.html" class="block bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg flex items-center space-x-4 shadow hover:bg-gray-100">
      <div class="text-yellow-600 text-2xl">🔒</div>
      <div>
        <h4 class="font-semibold">Change Password</h4>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Update your password</p>
      </div>

    <!-- Logout -->
    <a href="login.html" onclick="logout()" class="block bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg flex items-center space-x-4 shadow hover:bg-gray-100">
      <div class="text-red-600 text-2xl">🚪</div>
      <div>
        <h4 class="font-semibold">Logout</h4>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Security sign out</p>
      </div>
    </a>
  </div>

  <script>
    const name = localStorage.getItem("loggedInUser") || "Unknown User";
    const profilePic = localStorage.getItem("loggedInUserPicture");

    document.getElementById("userName").textContent = name;

    if (profilePic) {
      document.getElementById("profileImage").src = profilePic;
    }

    function logout() {
      localStorage.clear(); // Clears all user data
      window.location.href = "login.html";
    }

    // Save Nickname
    document.getElementById("saveNickname").addEventListener("click", function() {
      const newNickname = document.getElementById("nickname").value;
      if (newNickname) {
        localStorage.setItem("loggedInUser", newNickname); // Save new nickname
        document.getElementById("userName").textContent = newNickname; // Update on page
      }
    });

    // Brightness Adjustment
    const brightnessSlider = document.getElementById("brightnessSlider");
    const brightnessValue = document.getElementById("brightnessValue");

    brightnessSlider.addEventListener("input", function() {
      document.body.style.filter = `brightness(${brightnessSlider.value}%)`;
      brightnessValue.textContent = `${brightnessSlider.value}%`;
    });

    // Font Size Adjustment
    const fontSizeSlider = document.getElementById("fontSizeSlider");
    const fontSizeValue = document.getElementById("fontSizeValue");

    fontSizeSlider.addEventListener("input", function() {
      document.body.style.fontSize = fontSizeSlider.value + "px";
      fontSizeValue.textContent = fontSizeSlider.value + "px";
    });
  </script>
</body>
</html>

Changes made:

  1. Dark Mode: The dark mode toggle functionality has been removed.

  2. Nickname: Users can change their nickname, and the change will be reflected on the page and saved in localStorage.

  3. Brightness: A brightness slider (0-200%) has been added to control the overall brightness of the page.

  4. Font Size: A slider allows users to adjust the font size dynamically.

Let me know if you'd like further adjustments!

        document.getElementById("userName").textContent = newNickname; // Update on page
      }
    });

    // Brightness Adjustment
    const brightnessSlider = document.getElementById("brightnessSlider");
    const brightnessValue = document.getElementById("brightnessValue");

    brightnessSlider.addEventListener("input", function() {
      document.body.style.filter = `brightness(${brightnessSlider.value}%)`;
      brightnessValue.textContent = `${brightnessSlider.value}%`;
    });

    // Font Size Adjustment
    const fontSizeSlider = document.getElementById("fontSizeSlider");
    const fontSizeValue = document.getElementById("fontSizeValue");

    fontSizeSlider.addEventListener("input", function() {
      document.body.style.fontSize = fontSizeSlider.value + "px";
      fontSizeValue.textContent = fontSizeSlider.value + "px";
    });

    // Toggle Privacy Settings visibility
    document.getElementById("privacySettings").addEventListener("click", function() {
      const privacyContent = document.getElementById("privacyContent");
      privacyContent.classList.toggle("hidden");
    });
  </script>
</body>
